[l] Aus der beliebten Serie "Trump verkackt mal wieder was", heute: Der Flugzeugtraeger, den Trump nach Nordkorea geschickt hat.The problem was that the carrier, the Carl Vinson, and the three other warships in its strike force were that very moment sailing in the opposite direction, to take part in joint exercises with the Australian Navy in the Indian Ocean, 3,500 miles southwest of the Korean Peninsula.Und wie immer bei Trump ist jemand anderes schuld, naemlich das fiese Pentagon, das den armen unschuldigen Trump falsch informiert hat.
